sentences: Gille (ジル, Jiru, born January 4, 1987), stylized GILLE, is a Japanese singer originally from Saito, Miyazaki.
She made her major debut in 2012, but had previously performed under the name TASHA gee.

Gille made her debut with the album I AM GILLE.
